{"tid":1599570,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[入黎投票啦］得翻3日 你地究竟達成共識未？","createTime":"2019-09-28T05:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T07:22:32.000Z","uid":231478,"like":18,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c560e0720c512e4e07952b3fc2ae49335e9e763d","tid":1599570,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T05:03:30.000Z","msg":"10.1 <br />\n港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（琴日好似話係五區）<br />\n各有各搞就留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n琴日有風吹遍地開花，但之後又有風吹一定要港島 究竟想點？<br />\n依場運動<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">成功與否</span></span> 要睇我地能唔能夠<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">達成共識</span></span> 唔好比人成功分化我地<br />\n歡迎大家討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n勇武同和理非 都缺一不可<br />\n不分化 不篤灰 不割蓆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今晚見</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c4d47d1537cb4856400690c8dace7d98a2bd47","tid":1599570,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201